node.text:
Part 1 of 3 new brisket videos on our YouTube channel comparing different cook methods. We trimmed & seasoned 6 @44farms the same way and smoked them at 250° in the @mill.scale. 

I’m joined by my buddies @zavalasbarbecue & @jirby_bbq of @goldeesbbq to drop some knowledge and have an unbiased taste test at the end. We hope you enjoy this fun new series!

#MeatChurch #TexasBBQ #Brisket #44Farms #MillScale 📷: @katepraslickaphoto

node.title: Smoking Brisket wrapped in foil vs. Smoking Brisket wrapped in butcher pape

Pure Texas supper for @traciepittman & I tonight. Prime filet from @heb seasoned with our Holy Cow. Sous Vide in the @anovaculinary 90 @ 129°. Seared in hot cast iron 1 min per side for me & 2 min per side for the wife. Rested with Tuscan Herb butter also from @heb. Paired with @augustavinwinery Sagrantino from one of our favorite Texas wineries in Fredericksburg. This hit the spot!

node.text:
Key Lime Pie coming out of the @traegergrills. 

Our kids wanted to make something to help their Aunt Jordan feel better as she came home from the hospital after a fight with covid & pneumonia. 

I always say cooking is more fun when you get your kids involved. I can already tell Ava Belle is going to be a little boss lady in the kitchen. The only help she would let me give them was making the whip cream with a whisk (BEATING) because a beater went missing. 

Let me taste these before I put the recipe on meatchurch.com. I need to make sure they are edible but I know they smell good. Check our story for the highlights & swipe ➡️ to see their scratch process. 

#MeatChurch #BakeryChurch #Traeger #Traegerhood #KeyLimePie #KeyLime

node.text:
Well, that’s a wrap on the Pittman family vaca. We recharged in the mountains of Utah & then the beaches of Florida. Now it’s back to Texas & back to school for the kids. Sambo starts 3rd grade this week & Ava Belle is off to 5th. Time flies by so fast, so I’m grateful for every minute we get to spend together as a family. 

Shout out to @yeti for handling all our gear with ease and for turning every Dad head in every airport. 🔥

Hope y’all have a great week!

#MeatChurch #YETI #YETIBags
